{"tid":668701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少女聯絡簿爆「被爸朋友摸下面」　老師報警","createTime":"2018-05-18T00:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T18:34:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f6a54d7d92dfd0cdcfeb69785a899b40eb88c7","tid":668701,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:40:44.000Z","msg":"色膽包天，竟連朋友的女兒都下得了手！<br />\n<br />\n《聯合報》報導，王姓色男與被害國中少女父親熟識，平日就常常到她家泡茶聊天，前年7、8月期間，王男見少女獨自在客廳，竟趁她不注意時伸手觸摸她胸部，少女連忙閃開並表示「不要」，王男停手，並拿了100元要求少女保密；前年11月，王男又到少女家，又趁她不備時，伸手觸摸她的私處，少女閃躲後，王男即未再觸摸她。<br />\n<br />\n少女事後在學校聯絡簿上寫「遭爸爸朋友摸下面」等語，隔日老師批閱後報警處理，王男遭判1年2個月，他以15萬與少女家人達成和解，合議庭給予緩刑4年，並罰參加地檢署舉辦的法治教育15場。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180518/640_80ccd9f6839da46c63fa836569c40bc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180518%2F640_80ccd9f6839da46c63fa836569c40bc8.jpg&h=af3fc879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180518/1356162/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180518%2F1356162%2F&d=0lMTb%2Be1X1udiJY8OEQYvARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=65275019\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180518%2F1356162%2F&h=03f91ab8\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180518/1356162/</a>"},{"pid":"c1b150c41cd17b2131db4fbc54ee04373dd10e52","tid":668701,"uid":70227,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:42:33.000Z","msg":"所"},{"pid":"e0126dce3cd707e26f15100769c1a391ff07dcff","tid":668701,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T00:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7160de5a113ac1a23cc74be7173090bc7636919b","tid":668701,"uid":35598,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTi